{"tid":1840843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有香港人立即行動，停止食花生同打飛機！！！！！","createTime":"2020-01-25T04:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T11:54:56.000Z","uid":4396,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc41374f97d9fcc673138a1cf3aa04cb267761a","tid":1840843,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"個個淨係識po微博啲評論上黎，然後就笑9人，完全冇人討論點先可以令香港封閉邊境。<br />\n<br />\n你話醫護罷工就得？<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民三罷</span></span>呀！唔好將個責任推哂落醫護人員到，怪佢地唔罷工。咁耐以來，我地都係齊上齊落，依家香港生死存亡之際，我地更應該團結一致，一起對抗肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n1.立刻組織全民三罷<br />\n2.聯合十八區區議員，正式宣布香港進入緊急狀態<br />\n3.宣布全港學校停課<br />\n4.要求民陣組織遊行至高鐵<br />\n5.加強地區性消毒及衛生清潔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己香港自己救，我地唔可以再抱住隔岸觀火的態度面對肺炎，依個病毒已經殺到埋身！<br />\n<br />\n我地要同時間競賽！唔可以再拖落去！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民三罷，香港封關！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a2a4e602238f942ced5d11689f2a65bf8c96e8e1","tid":1840843,"uid":196450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1d81f95903d74626389d7f10bd24d1f8a092f121","tid":1840843,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1e45fe90b25d043395ae154d921e7e62735b8c7","tid":1840843,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e61a5b6c30759d00138d1661e9492350071ef49b","tid":1840843,"uid":4396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,